title: Super Vegetariano
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, Buffet, Salad bar, Take-out, Mexican
description: Vegetarian buffet offering different regional selections each day. Uses some dairy, but staff is knowledgeable about the ingredients. Fruit, water, and dessert are included in the $50 pesos all-you-can-eat buffet. Gets crowded after 2pm. Serves pizza on Sundays. Located three blocks from Bosque Cuauhtemoc.
